videos.description: Donovan Williams dribbles around the arc and buries a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Williams knocks down 3 for Texas) 2020/02/29

videos.headline: Williams knocks down 3 for Texas

videos.description: Texas Tech's Jahmi'us Ramsey feeds Kevin McCullar for a dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (McCullar throws down two-handed jam) 2020/02/29

videos.headline: McCullar throws down two-handed jam

videos.description: Texas uses good ball movement to get it to Courtney Ramey, who hits an off-balanced 3-pointer with five seconds on the shot clock.
videos.headline: Ramey sinks tough 3

videos.description: Texas Tech's Kyler Edwards gets a good look from way downtown and knocks down the 3 as the shot clock expires.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Edwards beats shot clock with 3 from the logo) 2020/02/29

videos.headline: Edwards beats shot clock with 3 from the logo

videos.description: Trailing by 4 points, Texas Tech's Jahmi'us Ramsey drives to the basket for a powerful slam, but misses it to seal the Red Raiders' fate.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Ramsey misses key slam for Texas Tech) 2020/02/29

videos.headline: Ramsey misses key slam for Texas Tech
